@dev L = sqrt(xy) = sqrt(k)
 Price = y / x
 L = sqrt(y / Price * y)
 L = sqrt(y^2 / Price) = y / sqrt(Price)
 L = sqrt(x * P * x)
 L = sqrt(x^2 * P)
 L = sqrt(x^2) * sqrt(P)
 L = x * sqrt(Price)
 x = L / sqrt(Price) <------- Use this to compute amount0
 y = L * sqrt(Price) <------- Use this to compute amount1
 liquidity = L = liquidity we want to mint
